aboutChannelInfo/channelDescription: I am a 20+ year beauty industry pro, that started this channel to share all of the makeup tips and tricks I have learned over the course of my career working for brands like Laura Mercier, Chanel, Bobbi Brown and more!  I review the latest makeup releases from Ulta, Sephora and the drugstore, and create in-depth, up close makeup tutorials, My focus is mature women who still want to look fashionable and beautiful over 40.  Easy to follow, hooded eye tutorials are my specialty, but I also love to share a bit of my love of fashion and travel. I has do much fun being a makeup artist for many years, but now I find joy in helping mature women look and feel their best and creating a supportive beauty-loving community online!

〰️T3 Curlers come with 4 large and 4 medium curlers

1️⃣ 1 large curler for my bangs rolled away from my face 

2️⃣ 1 large curler for back layers around my crown rolled toward the nape of the neck to create volume

3️⃣ 2 large curlers for face-framing layers rolled away from the face

4️⃣ 4 smaller curlers for bottom layers rolled away from face

5️⃣ Remove after ~20 minutes or when rollers have cooled

#curlers #curler #hairroutine #hairtutorial #bouncyhair #voluminoushair #morningroutines

aboutChannelInfo/channelDescription:
Hi there!

I'm Charlotte, a working mum in my 40s who just LOVES all things makeup and beauty. 
It's my passion, it's how I relax when I have some time to myself (rarely!) and my THERAPY!  
I started my channel for people like myself who want to share ideas, tips, products and obsessions with me and other make up and beauty lovers!
I upload every week as many times as I can, usually 3!!
I'm not a professional makeup artist, I just love playing with makeup, finding GREAT products that work for me and are flattering on my skin. Creating looks I can wear everyday to work, on the school run or on the odd occasion I'm going somewhere exciting!! I'd love for you to join my friendly , chatty, supportive and fun community here on YouTube!!  Can't wait to get to know you!! Xx

text:
I purchased @xerjoff Elle Anniversary without really knowing whether I would like it because THAT BOTTLE! And I was fairly safe as I've never met a @xerjoff I didn't love. But, luckily, it's the most beautiful juicy fruity concoction and the Litchi note is everything I hoped for. This will be a staple for me in summer 
Top Notes: Red Fruits, Green Apple, Litchi, Bergamot 
Middle Notes: Peony, Jasmine, Cashmere Wood, Liquorice 
Base Notes: Musk, Amber, Sandalwood, Patchouli
title: UNBOXING XERJOFF ELLE ANNIVERSARY

It's my passion, it's how I relax when I have some time to myself (rarely!) and my THERAPY!  
I started my channel for people like myself who want to share ideas, tips, products and obsessions with me and other make up and beauty lovers!
I upload every week as many times as I can, usually 3!!
I'm not a professional makeup artist, I just love playing with makeup, finding GREAT products that work for me and are flattering on my skin. Creating looks I can wear everyday to work, on the school run or on the odd occasion I'm going somewhere exciting!! I'd love for you to join my friendly , chatty, supportive and fun community here on YouTube!!  Can't wait to get to know you!! Xx

aboutChannelInfo/channelDescription: I am a 20+ year beauty industry pro, that started this channel to share all of the makeup tips and tricks I have learned over the course of my career working for brands like Laura Mercier, Chanel, Bobbi Brown and more!  I review the latest makeup releases from Ulta, Sephora and the drugstore, and create in-depth, up close makeup tutorials, My focus is mature women who still want to look fashionable and beautiful over 40.  Easy to follow, hooded eye tutorials are my specialty, but I also love to share a bit of my love of fashion and travel. I has do much fun being a makeup artist for many years, but now I find joy in helping mature women look and feel their best and creating a supportive beauty-loving community online!

aboutChannelInfo/channelDescription:
Hi there!

I'm Charlotte, a working mum in my 40s who just LOVES all things makeup and beauty. 
It's my passion, it's how I relax when I have some time to myself (rarely!) and my THERAPY!
